</ol><!-- .children -->
</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment even depth-2 comment-item">
		<article id="comment-36704" class="comment-block">
			<header class="comment-header">
				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/89cf6952d333a81fe6a7d3a64248f676?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">Théo31</cite>
				<a class="comment-permalink" href="http://h16free.com/2011/05/12/8292-la-petition-des-fabricants-de-photos/comment-page-1#comment-36704" title="19 h 56 min"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-05-17T19:56:52+00:00">17 mai 2011, 19 h 56 min</time></a>			</header>

			
			<div class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Des centaines de métiers ont disparu et la Terre continue de tourner. Si les photographes n&rsquo;ont pas compris que leur métier, ce n&rsquo;est plus uniquement de l&rsquo;impression sur papier, tant pis pour eux !</p>
			</div>
			<div class="comment-action">
				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/05/12/8292-la-petition-des-fabricants-de-photos?replytocom=36704#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-36704", "36704", "respond", "8292")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
